<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <title>Even Odd</title>
</head>
<body>
    <script>
        var num = 59;
        if(num % 2 == 0){
            console.log(num + " is even number");
        }
        else{
            console.log(num + " is odd number");
        }
    </script>
</body>
</html>

OUTPUT :
59 is odd number
